{"title":"IBM品牌设计 | 用渐变色阐释量子计算","slug":"pux575zp1hkvf5ur","summary":"核心设计理念在于将量子计算的抽象概念转化为 动态、可生成 的视觉语言，而非传统的静态品牌标识。具体而言，该设计理念包含以下几个核心方面： 1. 将抽象科学原理转化为视觉语言 该项目最关键的设计理念，是将量子计算的三大核心原理—— 叠加态（Superposition）、纠缠态（En","category":"1. 海外产品","tags":["PART6️⃣ AI产品设计案例分析库","1. 海外产品"],"featured":false,"order":91,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2025-09-14","wordCount":583,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/pux575zp1hkvf5ur","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"ud958cd51\" id=\"ud958cd51\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9f47ac95\" id=\"u9f47ac95\">核心设计理念在于将量子计算的抽象概念转化为</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u230b5c76\" id=\"u230b5c76\">动态、可生成</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u19e2b5e1\" id=\"u19e2b5e1\">的视觉语言，而非传统的静态品牌标识。具体而言，该设计理念包含以下几个核心方面：</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22XINpH%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"a02939f1\" id=\"a02939f1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u121eca55\" id=\"u121eca55\">1. 将抽象科学原理转化为视觉语言</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u6a93e9d3\" id=\"u6a93e9d3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7609ddbb\" id=\"u7609ddbb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">该项目最关键的设计理念，是将量子计算的三大核心原理——</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u693671b8\" id=\"u693671b8\">叠加态（Superposition）、纠缠态（Entanglement）和干涉态（Interference）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1c7b7f46\" id=\"u1c7b7f46\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">——作为视觉生成工具的参数。这种方法让原本难以理解的科学概念变得具象化和可感知。</span></p><ul list=\"u18c29511\"><li fid=\"u53c392fb\" data-lake-id=\"u68a8e462\" id=\"u68a8e462\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf1c8c735\" id=\"uf1c8c735\">叠加态</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0bce2ac7\" id=\"u0bce2ac7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">的视觉化可能表现为元素的层叠或共存。</span></li><li fid=\"u53c392fb\" data-lake-id=\"ud9fa3f8f\" id=\"ud9fa3f8f\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1a8aca75\" id=\"u1a8aca75\">纠缠态</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u85e47474\" id=\"u85e47474\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">可能通过相互关联、彼此影响的线条或形态来呈现。</span></li><li fid=\"u53c392fb\" data-lake-id=\"ub6876621\" id=\"ub6876621\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6eb83139\" id=\"u6eb83139\">干涉态</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u84983032\" id=\"u84983032\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">则可能通过元素间的相互作用，产生独特的波纹或图案。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ucf43f83b\" id=\"ucf43f83b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1a92b2c8\" id=\"u1a92b2c8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">这种设计方法使品牌视觉的“DNA”与量子计算本身的科学原理紧密相连。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22r0GXS%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"636065bb\" id=\"636065bb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3b98435a\" id=\"u3b98435a\">2. 生成式与算法驱动的设计</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u589fdec3\" id=\"u589fdec3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u78a3fb2c\" id=\"u78a3fb2c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">与传统依赖设计师手工创作不同，该项目采用了一个</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue332303b\" id=\"ue332303b\">生成式品牌工具</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3fa3e3dd\" id=\"u3fa3e3dd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">。这意味着视觉效果并非预先设计好的，而是由算法实时生成的。这种设计理念与量子计算的适应性和可扩展性相呼应，使得品牌视觉可以无限变化，但又始终保持统一的风格和内在逻辑。它不是一个单一的视觉作品，而是一个能够持续创造新作品的“视觉系统”。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22G8u1K%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"b97c2bad\" id=\"b97c2bad\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2458ced7\" id=\"u2458ced7\">3. 数据驱动的个性化体验</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u045a6878\" id=\"u045a6878\"><span data-lake-id=\"u107a2811\" id=\"u107a2811\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">在为2023年IBM量子峰会设计视觉时，该项目将数据驱动的理念融入其中。设计师利用参会者的位置数据，为每人生成了独一无二的个性化视觉图像，并印制在他们的胸卡和邀请函上。这不仅是一种创新，更体现了品牌与用户之间独特的、一对一的互动关系，将抽象的品牌理念转化为每个人的专属体验。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6635af12\" id=\"u6635af12\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1757844933425-b9f919a3-79d3-4310-96d2-88e5ef8e5fec.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uaff7d8ec-3dd5-4a51-97b0-14b9bc56479%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u02fa5226-5792-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A6000%2C%22height%22%3A4001%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A2560%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1707%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23d8d7d5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u69604b0d%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: transparent\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub5b2feee\" id=\"ub5b2feee\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1757844935144-10809ddb-f31e-4680-a819-9fff905a88ff.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u49e94f96-17e6-437d-9f1c-08d7ffa265d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u02fa5226-5792-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A777%2C%22height%22%3A1110%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A777%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1110%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%239699a4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u147bbad3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: transparent\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u57731d31\" id=\"u57731d31\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1757844933212-607aea11-1756-4ed6-ad9c-e9f2fe2eaac5.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua21db387-d5c3-4f1e-95e5-37ab9430a91%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u02fa5226-5792-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A543%2C